overview: Yeah, that's me in Real College Girls #3. Crazy, huh? I went from Feminism 101 to my first facial in just a semester. After meeting that crazy chick Candy Cooze and her creepy boss Bob Sima, I've been completely transformed. All the cocksucking and boning that I've been doing has made me the most popular chick on campus. Real College Girls #3 was more than just a paycheck. It was a sexual awakening. My eighteenth birthday made me a woman, but it was college that made me a whore.
title: Real College Girls 3
